import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import TodoContainer from "./components/TodoContainer"
import "./App.css"
import { BrowserRouter, Router, Routes } from "react-router-dom"



ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Routes>
    <Router>
      <TodoContainer />
    </Router>  
    </Routes>
  </React.StrictMode>, 
  document.getElementById("root")
);
